
SALVA: MACRO &ORIGEM, &DESTINO
       COPY &ORIGEM, &DESTINO
       ENDMACRO

BACKUP: MACRO &VAR
        SALVA &VAR, TEMP
        ENDMACRO

PROGRAMA: INPUT NUM1
          INPUT NUM2
          BACKUP NUM1
          LOAD NUM2
          STORE NUM1
          OUTPUT NUM1
          STOP

NUM1: SPACE
NUM2: SPACE
TEMP: SPACE
